 ## Dependency direction
 
 Strictly top-to-bottom: presentation → application → domain → infrastructure. No upward imports. The current code mostly respects this; deviations should be flagged in PR review.
+
+**Shared valuation:** `bot/live_portfolio.py` is imported by `engine.py`, `watchdog/engine.py`, `dashboard/parsers/`, and `bot/auditor/context.py` — keep price-merge logic there rather than duplicating.
